CSS Animations

Research the following questions and create a medium blog post. Please link any and all references made within your blog.

---------------------------------------------------

1. In your own words explain CSS animations?

2. Give an example of an animation. (Show code example and explain what the animation is doing).

3. How can CSS animations be used with Javascript?

4. In your own words explain CSS Transform.

5. Give an example of transform.

6. Explain the difference between animation and transform.


